To enroll in the classes, student must login first (create an account if it doesn't exist).


[Use Case A] ============== How do students enroll in classes?


[1] Login first

[2] Enroll (in one class)  (students can register for only one class)

[3] Set Communication Preferences
-- parent 1 email and phone number
-- parent 2 email and phone number

[4] Pay the fee


